 classical degeneracy\nof different spiral ground states. Implications for (CuCl)LaNb2O7 and related\ncompounds are discussed in light of our theoretical results and existing\nexperimental data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Apr 2011 20:00:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 28 Apr 2011 19:25:26 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 16 Aug 2011 08:12:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-08-17"}
